						<div class="postbody">For what it's worth, Kasumi -- my own feelings mimic many of your own.  So don't feel alone in things like laughing at Kickstarter budgets, or the lot of idealists who have no actual skill set to achieve what they propose (or the finances to do so -- or more importantly, even knowing the people who can make those realities happen (i.e. they know nobody)), as well as being frustrated by &quot;simple things&quot; like drawing + erasing a &quot;window&quot; on the NES (I absolutely can see how that would take 3 weeks.  Hell, it'd probably have taken me more like 2-3 months -- it's really not a simple task, there's a lot that has to be tracked internally).</div>

